text: Linkou (林口) may refer to: ==Mainland China== *Linkou County, of Mudanjiang, Heilongjiang *Linkou, Heilongjiang, county seat of Linkou County *Linkou, Guizhou, town in Qixingguan District, Bijie ==Taiwan== *Linkou District, rural district of New Taipei *Linkou Line, railway branch line, located in Taoyuan County and New Taipei *Linkou Station, station on the Linkou Line in Linkou District, New Taipei *New Taipei Municipal Lin-kou High School (formerly National Linkou High School), a high school in Linkou District, New Taipei
title: Linkou
